headline: Stifel Lifts PT on Analog Devices (ADI), Maintains Buy Rating Ahead of Earnings Tomorrow
summary: On May 20, Stifel lifted the price target on Analog Devices Inc. (NASDAQ:ADI) from $225 to $248, maintaining its Buy rating on the stock. Tore Svanberg from Stifel increased the price target on ADI ahead of its earnings tomorrow. Analog Devices will report its earnings for the second quarter of 2025 before the market opening […]
